        <Paragraph>
          <span> Creating exceptional web experiences for your users</span><br
          />
          <span>
            Maintaining and improving your existing suite of Web Applications
          </span><br />
          <span>
            Taking ownership of projects and driving them to successful
            completion
          </span><br />
          <span
            >Managing and maintaining eCommerce and CMS (Content Mangment
            Systems)</span
          ><br />
        </Paragraph>
      </div> -->
    </ServiceOffer>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <Service
        title="Project management"
        description="A website requires a project manager to plan the website, manage developers, designers and writers to collaborate and build a website that meets your expectations."
      >
        <span slot="icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-6 h-6"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M6 12L3.269 3.126A59.768 59.768 0 0121.485 12 59.77 59.77 0 013.27 20.876L5.999 12zm0 0h7.5"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </Service>
      <Service
        title="Site Structure"
        description="Planning out your site structure and how your web pages will link together will help Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) to understand what your website is about, enabling more people to find you. "
      >
        <span slot="icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-6 h-6"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M6 12L3.269 3.126A59.768 59.768 0 0121.485 12 59.77 59.77 0 013.27 20.876L5.999 12zm0 0h7.5"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </Service>
      <Service
        title="Design"
        description="Good web design will capture your visitors' attention and map out a good user experience while clearly understanding the benefits that your service offers. Great design converts visitors to customers."
      >
        <span slot="icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-6 h-6"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M6 12L3.269 3.126A59.768 59.768 0 0121.485 12 59.77 59.77 0 013.27 20.876L5.999 12zm0 0h7.5"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </Service>
      <Service
        title="Development"
        description="Programing your website design into a fully functional website that looks good on all devices, including smartphones and tablets while ensuring fast loading speeds. "
      >
        <span slot="icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-6 h-6"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M6 12L3.269 3.126A59.768 59.768 0 0121.485 12 59.77 59.77 0 013.27 20.876L5.999 12zm0 0h7.5"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </Service>
      <Service
        title="Testing"
        description="A part of development is testing your website thoroughly to make sure there are no bugs and pages with errors. This is essential to ensure a smooth user experience for your visitors."
      >
        <span slot="icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-6 h-6"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M6 12L3.269 3.126A59.768 59.768 0 0121.485 12 59.77 59.77 0 013.27 20.876L5.999 12zm0 0h7.5"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </Service>
      <Service
        title="Maintenance"
        description="All websites have ongoing maintenance costs including domain name renewal, SSL certificate renewal, website security and any plugins or themes your website uses."
      >
        <span slot="icon">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
            class="w-6 h-6"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M6 12L3.269 3.126A59.768 59.768 0 0121.485 12 59.77 59.77 0 013.27 20.876L5.999 12zm0 0h7.5"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </Service>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
